OL,3,CAI could be used to detect heart
OL,4,Cfailure risk, study finds
OL,6,FArtificial intelligence could be used
OL,7,Fto help detect people living with the
OL,8,Frisk of experiencing heart failure,
OL,9,Faccording to a study.
OL,11,FResearchers at the University of
OL,12,FDundee's School of Medicine used
OL,13,Fartificial intelligence (AI) to scan
OL,14,Fimages of the heart to identify
OL,15,Fpatients with heart failure from
OL,16,Fpopulation based electronic health
OL,17,Frecords and echocardiography heart
OL,18,Fscans.
