OL,6,FAI deep learning was then used to
OL,7,Fexamine echocardiographic images to
OL,8,Fidentify anomalies that could increase
OL,9,Fa patient's risk.
OL,11,FExperts used data made available by
OL,12,Fpatients voluntarily through the
OL,13,FScottish Health Research Register and
OL,14,FBiobank (SHARE), which provides
OL,15,Fresearchers with volunteers, samples,
OL,16,Fhealth data and genomic information
OL,17,Ffor clinical trials.
