OL,3,CAI could be used to detect heart
OL,4,Cfailure risk, study finds
OL,6,FThe process began with a dataset of
OL,7,F15,000 patient records which was
OL,8,Fnarrowed down to a cohort of 578
OL,9,Fpatients.
OL,11,FProfessor Chim Lang said: "Our
OL,12,Fresearch represents an advancement in
OL,13,Fthe utilisation of deep learning to
OL,14,Fautomatically interpret
OL,15,Fechocardiographic images. This can
OL,16,Fallow us to streamline the
OL,17,Fidentification of patients with heart
OL,18,Ffailure at scale within electronic
OL,19,Fhealth record datasets.
