OL,4,Cfailure risk, study finds
OL,6,F"Echocardiography heart scans that
OL,7,Fwere enhanced by the AI software
OL,8,Fhelped to provide more measurements `
OL,9,For parameters ` of heart structure and
OL,10,Ffunction that can be used to help
OL,11,Fdiagnose heart failure.
OL,13,F"These measurements were not routinely
OL,14,Freported by the usual heart scans from
OL,15,Fthe electronic health records.
OL,17,F"When compared to reports generated by
OL,18,Froutine heart scans, those enhanced by
OL,19,FAI were more detailed and could also
OL,20,Fbe processed at a larger scale than
OL,21,Fconventional images.
