OL,6,F"This has potential clinical and
OL,7,Fresearch implications as it could
OL,8,Fenhance the efficiency and speed of
OL,9,Fpatient selection for pragmatic
OL,10,Fclinical trials, as well as improving
OL,11,Fheart failure surveillance and early
OL,12,Fdiagnosis across hospital systems."
OL,14,FExperts said heart failure is a highly
OL,15,Fprevalent but under-diagnosed
OL,16,Fcondition that means the heart is
OL,17,Funable to pump blood around the body
OL,18,Feffectively.
