OL,3,CAI could be used to detect heart
OL,4,Cfailure risk, study finds
OL,6,FWhile symptoms can be controlled to
OL,7,Fsome extent through lifestyle changes,
OL,8,Fsurgery and medication, in most
OL,9,Finstances it is a serious, long-term
OL,10,Fcondition that gets progressively
OL,11,Fworse over time.
OL,13,FProf Lang said the latest research is
OL,14,F"an example of how AI has the
OL,15,Fpotential to provide real-world
OL,16,Fbenefits to patients".
