OL,6,FHe said: "By assessing vast amounts of
OL,7,Fpatient records, we have been able to
OL,8,Fdetect structural and functional
OL,9,Fanomalies that we would not have been
OL,10,Fable to do with traditional analysis
OL,11,Fof echocardiographic images.
OL,13,F"While this is a test case, I'm very
OL,14,Fexcited that we have been able to
OL,15,Fapply deep learning to a biobank
OL,16,Fresource on a large scale.
OL,18,F"Hopefully this paves the way for
OL,19,Fother researchers to utilise this
OL,20,Ftechnology to benefit patients around
OL,21,Fthe world."
